    h2.govuk-heading-m id="about-the-service" About the Service
    p
      | The Service is used by Trading Standards and other market surveillance authorities (MSAs) to report, track
        and share product safety information. It has been developed alongside people from these organisations by the
        digital team at the OPSS.
    p
      ' The Service has been designed for use by Trading Standards officers and people from other market surveillance
        authorities (MSAs). You need to belong to one of those organisations and be a registered user to
      = link_to "log in", keycloak_login_url
      |  and access the Service.

