    p
      | We do not guarantee that the Service, or any content on it, will always be available or be uninterrupted.
        We may suspend or withdraw or restrict the availability of all or any part of the Service for business
        and operational reasons. We will try to give you reasonable notice of any suspension or withdrawal.
    p
      | You are also responsible for ensuring that all persons who access the Service through your
        internet connection are aware of these Terms and other applicable terms and conditions
        and that they comply with them.

